{"tid":1561863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(本土思潮，勇武抗爭)港人正在追隨梁天琦的理念","createTime":"2019-09-11T18:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T20:01:32.000Z","uid":259583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02be58be03d6fece4e2b90362c54c154ec7bf302","tid":1561863,"uid":259583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">梁天琦：一場激烈既體制轉變就係革命。</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係五年前既雨傘革命入面我其實同港豬無分別，雖然係支持抗爭者，表態左係黃絲，亦明白果次公民抗命既起承轉合，但我仍然係一個無出過去，政治冷感既高中學生。當時，我覺得對呢個有中共極權支撐既港共政權黎講，公民抗命亦係無果。<br />\n<br />\n今年五月幾，逃犯條例既影響比人分析，煲大。曾經既港豬們，包括我，猶如溫水煮蛙中既青蛙，突然辨識到危機將近，於是拼命爭扎，想跳出突然之間滾起既水。而覺得死到臨頭，做咩都冇用啦；或者係覺得呢d政治野唔關我事既港豬，真係無野可以再講，繼續係豬欄中被餵食啦。<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n你唔係廢青，唔係狗雄，亦唔係英雄，係一個革命先驅者。香港有良知，見識之士都會等你出番黎，同我地一齊掀起時代革命。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iD8jTLBJ8vI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiD8jTLBJ8vI&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a1665139\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iD8jTLBJ8vI</a><br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n天琦: 但係我唔明白既地方係我地呢d雞蛋面對高牆，奮不顧身咁撞埋去，點解你地要責備我地係暴力? 村上春樹去講呢句說話既時侯，佢係話雞蛋係每一個獨立的個體；高牆係制度既暴力。無論雞蛋點錯都好，佢永遠都會企係雞蛋果邊。我唔明白社會運動點解一次又一次去對抗呢個制度的暴力既時候，你地(泛民左膠道德撚)要去割席，反對我地既暴力，我地唔係為光環，唔係為左自己既利益，係覺得社會上有不公義我地要對抗。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋: 你有冇考慮過係你所帶領既呢d(對抗制度造成既不公義既)社會運動中，有無辜既香港人被波及，究竟作為領導底參與呢d運動既人，有冇一個道德責任呢?<br />\n天琦: 我願意負上所有責任，我自己本身唔想波及無辜者，但就是因為議事堂中的從政者無法解決社會既矛盾.，不能建設一個和諧的社會，所以我地先被逼於走上街頭。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋: 係咪應該要有底線?<br />\n天琦: 我自己係唔會有任何底線比自己，當比任何底線比自己去同呢個極權政府博鬥無疑是作繭自斃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uGUaAGtUGZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuGUaAGtUGZ4&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a3788b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uGUaAGtUGZ4</a><br />\n<br />\n係呢場革命入面，無論勇武做任何事情去對抗這個港共政權，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不篤灰，不割席原則不變!</span></span><br />\n中立撚同道德撚可以收下皮先 多謝合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f69f5fff660b4613902dab960447641f82f941b","tid":1561863,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:24:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2602aef1dd624d720a8b095895f88ac7b295718b","tid":1561863,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7f1e468aefdb5fabee40f277b395dfcd50a7977c","tid":1561863,"uid":295629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6b9d550fc20c2b5549802dbc8f59bf5b89d4a2","tid":1561863,"uid":36325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"聽親呢個版本既18 真係好SAD..."},{"pid":"97dd1aa00913e09acc4ee97029320d54e0763175","tid":1561863,"uid":259583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf6b9d550fc20c2b5549802dbc8f59bf5b89d4a2","tid":1561863,"uid":36325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"聽親呢個版本既18 真係好SAD..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T20:01:32.000Z","msg":"第一次睇果陣喊左"}]}